label: SemiosisMismatchQuestionSpecific

label: SemiosisMismatchQuestionGeneric

label: TyCorWordNet

label: TyCorLisTyCor_HEADWORD_LatToType

label: TyCorWikiCatDb_HEADWORD_LatToType+PersonDisambiguated+WordNet

label: TyCorIntroCor_HEADWORD_LatToType+WordNetDisambiguated

label: TyCorTheHutt

label: TyCorWordNetAnySense

label: PassageTermMatchInFocus-negation-excluded

label: PassageTermMatchInFocus-negation-penalty
